content: Howdy! My name is Sydney Brand, and I’m a sophomore Biomedical Science major from Lucas, Texas (A-A-A-A-A)! My hobbies include sports, dancing/singing, blasting music WAYY too loud in my car, and being one of the bros. I’m SO excited to be a co-chair of the Promo Committee this next year, and I cannot wait to meet all of you! T’s and G’s!!
